{"tid":685191,"cid":22,"subCid":0,"title":"Notebook HDD 換 SSD 一問","createTime":"2018-05-31T08:26:30.000Z","updateTime":"2018-06-01T02:45:00.000Z","uid":82970,"like":4,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":10,"replies":[{"pid":"aa95bacb8b046c9fec3fa33a8b6e7b546f7bad2a","tid":685191,"uid":82970,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-31T08:26:30.000Z","msg":"我有部買咗差唔多兩年既 Dell notebook <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 有3年保養<br />\n本野冇咩問題，只係 512 GB HDD load 野太慢，有時 lag 機都係因為佢<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/itdog2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n因為用得好唔爽，於是想換隻SSD入去，但入面剩係得一個 SATA III port <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/scare.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n諗緊可能買隻 512GB samsung 860 PRO SATA 擺入去<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/lick.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n但隻 SSD 其實壽命隨時長過部 notebook ，未來趨勢係 M.2 同 PCIE ，如果第時買 notebook 應該都會行 M.2 或 PCIE SSD，咁我依隻 SATA SSD 將來咪等同冇用<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/scare.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/scare.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 屋企又冇 desktop唔會用得著<br />\n市面上好多新插口轉舊插口，咁我想問下如果我買隻 samsung M.2 970 PRO 配 M.2 轉 SATA 轉換器得唔得<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/run.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 價錢差唔多，定係都係買返 SATA 860 PRO 算?"},{"pid":"a52ebf7f1628289fb9892b4111d2dfdb4ddf5e55","tid":685191,"uid":143411,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-05-31T10:33:45.000Z","msg":"有冇詳情型號 幫你check下"},{"pid":"20d34f94aab7ae80bbe4cc8c8616ef64f0767577","tid":685191,"uid":39225,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-05-31T10:56:26.000Z","msg":"m.2 pcie ssd轉唔到sata 可以省返<br />\n除非係m.2 sata ssd 就可以轉sata，但咁樣不如唔好買m.2"},{"pid":"a37295460ab23db3eec06491802c9fdf500f9925","tid":685191,"uid":147026,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-05-31T11:48:12.000Z","msg":"你話得一個SATA位，咁你Notebook本身有冇CD ROM位？有嘅拆出來加個HDD adapter ，咪可以用SSD 裝System 又可以用返HDD裝資料！<br />\n<br />\nM.2 SSD快就係因爲用咗PCIE，俾你轉到SATA即係廢咗武功，何必呢！"},{"pid":"61fb1c8cfdcd33157d79b4fa361ae126e6c1bafe","tid":685191,"uid